      <hedline>
        <hl1>MORE HOMELESS</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Pam Belluck</byline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A United States Conference of Mayors survey of 27 cities showed homelessness had increased an average of 13 percent from last year. The likeliest causes: recession, still-high housing prices and Sept. 11, which increased layoffs and diverted charitable donations that usually support shelters and other homeless organizations.</p>
        <p>Pam Belluck</p>
      </block>
